---
// CostComparison.astro — Serverless vs container cost at different scales
---
<div class="cc-wrap">
  <h3 class="cc-title">Cost at Scale — When Serverless Gets Expensive</h3>
  <div class="cc-chart">
    <div class="cc-row"><span class="cc-reqs">1K req/day</span><div class="cc-bars"><div class="cc-bar cc-bar--sl" style="--w:8%"><span class="cc-cost">$0.05</span></div><div class="cc-bar cc-bar--ct" style="--w:40%"><span class="cc-cost">$2.50</span></div></div></div>
    <div class="cc-row"><span class="cc-reqs">100K req/day</span><div class="cc-bars"><div class="cc-bar cc-bar--sl" style="--w:20%"><span class="cc-cost">$5</span></div><div class="cc-bar cc-bar--ct" style="--w:40%"><span class="cc-cost">$2.50</span></div></div></div>
    <div class="cc-row"><span class="cc-reqs">1M req/day</span><div class="cc-bars"><div class="cc-bar cc-bar--sl" style="--w:55%"><span class="cc-cost">$45</span></div><div class="cc-bar cc-bar--ct" style="--w:35%"><span class="cc-cost">$8</span></div></div></div>
    <div class="cc-row"><span class="cc-reqs">10M req/day</span><div class="cc-bars"><div class="cc-bar cc-bar--sl" style="--w:90%"><span class="cc-cost">$380</span></div><div class="cc-bar cc-bar--ct" style="--w:45%"><span class="cc-cost">$25</span></div></div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="cc-legend"><span class="cc-leg cc-leg--sl">■ Serverless (Lambda)</span><span class="cc-leg cc-leg--ct">■ Containers (Fargate 0.25vCPU)</span></div>
  <div class="cc-note">The crossover point is typically around 500K-1M requests/day for average workloads. Below that, serverless wins on cost. Above that, containers win. But factor in ops time — containers need someone to manage them.</div>
</div>
<style>
  .cc-wrap{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f172a,#1e293b);border-radius:16px;padding:2rem;margin:2rem 0;border:1px solid #334155}
  .cc-title{color:#f1f5f9;font-size:1.15rem;font-weight:700;margin:0 0 1.5rem}
  .cc-chart{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:14px;margin-bottom:1rem}
  .cc-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px}.cc-reqs{color:#94a3b8;font-size:.68rem;font-family:monospace;min-width:90px;text-align:right}
  .cc-bars{flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:4px}
  .cc-bar{height:16px;border-radius:6px;display:flex;align-items:center;padding-left:8px;width:0;animation:ccBar 1.2s ease forwards}
  .cc-bar--sl{background:rgba(6,182,212,.3);border:1px solid #06b6d450}.cc-bar--ct{background:rgba(129,140,248,.3);border:1px solid #818cf850}
  @keyframes ccBar{to{width:var(--w)}}
  .cc-cost{color:#e2e8f0;font-size:.58rem;font-family:monospace;font-weight:600;white-space:nowrap}
  .cc-legend{display:flex;gap:16px;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:10px}
  .cc-leg{font-size:.62rem;font-family:monospace}.cc-leg--sl{color:#06b6d4}.cc-leg--ct{color:#818cf8}
  .cc-note{color:#94a3b8;font-size:.7rem;line-height:1.6;padding:10px 14px;background:rgba(0,0,0,.15);border-radius:8px;border:1px solid #334155}
</style>
